name: Longing
description:
In this fast paced world, what do we long for?

For me personally, the feeling of peace is one of the hardest and most sought after state of mind. A contentment to what we have in life.  Being happy with what’s in front of us.

That is what I am longing for.

Media:
Kodak Tri-X 400 Film with an Olympus Pen FT Half Frame Camera
